---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                               |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer                                                         |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                     |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score    |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[answer, id, score]                                                                          |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer]                                                                                                              |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                 |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@2 as answer, score@1 as score]                                                                                        |
|               |       HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, on=[(id@0, id@1), (question@1, question@2)], projection=[id@0, score@2, answer@3]                            |
|               |         CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                     |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[union_extract(json_get(key@0, id), int) as id, union_extract(json_get(key@0, question), str) as question, 1 - distance@1 as score] |
|               |             CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                        |
|               |               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                 |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                   CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                     S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=30                                                                                                                   |
|               |         SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                         |
|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                       |
|               |             DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
